{"tid":769301,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"謝拉特：踢10個仲好","createTime":"2018-08-06T05:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T06:24:33.000Z","uid":153600,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bd5e283d1a047a5fbc27662bc110b3cf7c263a42","tid":769301,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:32:16.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=LVVB0e%2B3Hps28BqBYmZ8KARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=00c382f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】格拉斯哥流浪周日蘇超被鴨巴甸逼和1:1，首次領軍的新帥謝拉特豪氣表示：「踢10個表現反而更好！」<br />\n<br />\n利物浦神奇隊長謝拉特（Steven Gerrard）首次擔任一隊主帥，新球季將成為格流主帥，首場蘇超差點踢少1人之下全取3分，惜好夢成空，賽後表示：「我們表現無與倫比，甚至在10人應戰時，表現比11人更出色。」<br />\n<br />\n「鴨巴甸根本一籌莫展，我們至少比他們高一皮，每個球員都八面玲瓏，在93分鐘的比賽表現完美，最後未能贏波，但也為球員表現感到高興，也沒有半點失望。」謝拉特補充道。<br />\n<br />\n38歲的謝四在2016年掛靴，蘇超開咧前已率領格流在歐霸盃外圍賽連過2關，並暗示不排除為紅牌提出上訴：「有看比賽的球迷都明白，己隊肯定在鴨巴甸之上，尤其在進攻方面，事實上我們應可取得更多入球。或者，我們會上訴，但目前需要時間沉澱一下，冷靜下來再說。」"},{"pid":"f7590f6532ca0003858db64b5abbca77a53ae2aa","tid":769301,"uid":1977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"謝帥教下d教員40秒戰術咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee0c8deaf177b3750fde9bd6d8a036243b366db","tid":769301,"uid":6242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f7590f6532ca0003858db64b5abbca77a53ae2aa","tid":769301,"uid":1977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"謝帥教下d教員40秒戰術咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pU84Q5T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpU84Q5T.jpg&h=04649abe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0ebf56a17b6a6cb6f7b2bf0818be0d63a4bf319","tid":769301,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:24:33.000Z","msg":"挑戰羅渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}